<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وفي <span class="c2">(ص ٣٧٧)</span>: <span class="c1">"تالف"</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
